item.title: [317] OldskoolPK [317]
item.dc:creator: @im_not_rich im not rich
item.description:
@im_not_rich wrote:

kingcobra805:

m8 u need to add a file to make someone owner…you can only become admin otherwise its a awesome server.

If you mean that the Character file is missing, then you’re mistaking, because if it was missing, u couldn’t even run it or you dc, then it will give an error that it can’t put the new character somewhere,
And for if you don’t even know, because i just dled and character file was just in it,
Go into character file, Find your character, change the rights = 0 to rights = 3
Then you’re owner already…
And if you want to be the only owner even not the coder who made this, just look at his name, and replace it in all files.
And so you can do the staff commands, go into Commands.java, and Ctrl+h, type his name in top bar, and your name in the lower bar, and click “replace all”, then save & compile and you’re owner, mostly is there a line that shows a equalsignorecase " his name " and that means only he can do the commands under there,then just replace that name too, and you becoma the all-mighty command user.

:PAnd don’t say you already knew this otherwise you wouldn’t post such a dumb question about not being able to become owner
